my vimrc 
more details @http://lostjs.com/2012/02/04/use-pathogen-and-git-to-manage-vimfiles/
1 pathogen, @https://github.com/tpope/vim-pathogen
  plugin manager
  bundle/vim-pathogen

2 supertab, https://github.com/ervandew/supertab
  auto complete
  bundle/vim-supertab 

--------------
1 update plugin 
  single plugin updating, change dir to targit plugin dir: git checkout master; git pull
  all plugin updating: git submodule foreach 'git checkout master && git pull'

2 del plugin 
  rm -rf bundle/plugin
  git rm -r bundle/plugin

3 init plugin 
  git submodule add plugin_repository_in_git bundle/plugin_name
  example aboubt supertabr: git submodule add git@github.com:ervandew/supertab.git bundle/vim_supertab

